Book Chapter on Recommendation System
http://infolab.stanford.edu/~ullman/mmds/ch9.pdf

Slides companion to the above book chapter, my workshop is based on this slides
http://www.mmds.org/mmds/v2.1/ch09-recsys1.pdf

Article on Item-Item Collaborative Filtering by Amazon
http://www.cs.umd.edu/~samir/498/Amazon-Recommendations.pdf

Vignettes for R package recommenderlab, also a good read 
https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/recommenderlab/vignettes/recommenderlab.pdf

Crab - a python library for recommender system
http://muricoca.github.io/crab/

Graphlab also has a recommender system module (python as well)
https://dato.com/products/create/docs/graphlab.toolkits.recommender.html




